          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>August 25<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1853</date>.</p>
                              <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac
                                                  Leeser</addressee>  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Hebrew</add>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
                                        <placeName>164 Ludlow Street</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Hebrew</add>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N. Y.</placeName>
                                        <date>August 25, 1853</date>.</p>
                              <p><addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee>,
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
                              <p>Very honored friend:</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">You are the noble man who first drew the
                                        attention<lb/> and aroused the community of our land in the
                                        condition of the Jews of<lb/>
                                        <placeName>China</placeName>. All the communities from
                                                  <placeName>East</placeName> to
                                                  <placeName>West</placeName> have therefore
                                        expressed<lb/> the wish that as your agent I should occupy
                                        myself also with this<lb/> thing. They have therefore
                                        commissioned me to travel to
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> and have
                                        a committee organized by you in which you should act as
                                        pre-<lb/>sident. When I Passed through
                                                  <placeName>Albany</placeName>, <persName>Dr.
                                                  Wise</persName>
                                        <sic>madea</sic> suggestion, that<lb/> it would be to the
                                        best interests of the cause if you were to choose<lb/>
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName> as the organization point
                                        for this committee. He, too, wants<lb/> to contribute his
                                        share to this holy cause, and by word of mouth pre-<lb/>sent
                                        his completely formulated plans. On the <date>26<hi
                                                  rend="sup">th</hi></date> of this month, at<lb/> 6
                                        o'clock in the morning, he will arrive here and will wait
                                        for you <sic>t</sic><lb/> till <date>Monday</date> evening.
                                        I therefore beg of you, upon the receipt of this<lb/>
                                        letter, to let me know whether you will come or not. If you
                                        intend to<lb/> come, let me know beforehand where you intend
                                        to lodge, and bring along<lb/> for me 6 prayer books of the
                                        Ashkenazic ritual and 2 sets of pentateuchs<lb/> all bound.
                                        If you do not want to come, I shall go to
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> next<lb/> week
                                        and take these things along with me. Whether <persName>Dr.
                                                  Wise</persName> will make<lb/> the journey to
                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> or not, the
                                        other members of this community,<lb/> whom you are to name,
                                        will not make the journey. That <persName>Dr.
                                                  Wise</persName> will<lb/> deny revelation in his
                                        work, is a lie on the part of <add>?</add>......—a<lb/>
                                        brazen lie. On the contrary, everything is as it should
                                        be.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">Your eternal friend,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(7)">
                                        <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <placeName>164 Ludlow St.</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="On other side">It is self-understood that the cost of the
                                        trip will be returned to you,<lb/> and that only the
                                        “Occident” will be the organ in which the progress of<lb/>
                                        this thing will be revealed to the public.</p>
                              <pb n="Envelope"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>371 Walnut street</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">
                                        <placeName>Pa</placeName>
                              </p>
                    </body>
